=== Precinct shrines ===
Isorowa Shrine, Hachiman Shrine, Wakamatsu Shrine, Hachidai Shrine, Tennei Shrine, Kaminoki Shrine, Tsujinaka Shrine, Tenmangū-sha, Tenman Shrine

=== Precinct ===
* Monument to Tanemura Genpei (Horsehead commemorative stele)

=== Access ===
* From {{ill|lt=Kawase Station|Q614782|qid=Q614782|1=Kawase Station}} on the {{ill|lt=Biwako Line|Q804135|qid=Q804135|1=Biwako Line}} ({{ill|lt=Tōkaidō Main Line|Q1190152|qid=Q1190152|1=Tōkaidō Main Line}}), take the reservation-only Ainori Taxi Kawase to Kawasebabachō Kōminkan stop; 2 minutes on foot.
* About 12 minutes on foot from Kawase Station.

